<table width=100% border=0 cellspacing=10>
<tr><td bgcolor="#363636">
<a name="hammer_of_wrath"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Hammer of Wrath</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">1H Blunt</a><BR>
Damage per second - 4.06<BR>
Damage 6 - Delay 32<BR>
Weight: 5.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/paladin/weapons/1h_blunt.shtml">PAL</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) <BR>
</font>
Summoned by either a Cleric or a Paladin.<BR>

</td></tr>
