<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The only real use for this weapon is after you have been killed. Just mem this spell and summon yourself a magic weapon. It's nice not having to beg a small weapon off of some other player, and unless you've practiced your hand-to-hand combat (and what paladin or cleric does?) it's nice to have as you trek back to your body.</font></td></tr></table>
