<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Jaybird</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-07 19:04:39</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This weapon can also be weilded by a shaman.  The only way to do it is to do the Initiate Symbol of the Tribunal quest that starts in halas.  The quest is for shaman barbarian only and when you complete the quest you get the Symbol which is worn on the neck.  The effect of the Symbol is summon hammer of wrath.  It has unlimited charges and can be done as low a lvl as 4.  Great magic weapon for a newbie shaman.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Jaybird 12th lvl shaman<BR>
povar</font></td></tr></table>
